title: Carrier privileges
content:
Hello,
We are software developing team, and at this point we working on carrier-branded app to manage eSIM profiles, our carrier "Telia" listed in "android.googlesource.com carrier_list.textpb", we read this document, but can't get what exactly steps we need to get carrier privileges to control our esim profile, some steps feels missing https://source.android.com/devices/tech/config/uicc

Can we get contact with someone who can help us with getting "carrier privileges" for our app?
Thank you.
